paragraphs.text:
%vorathrift
CREATE PARTITION FUNCTION DOC_STORE_PF(X) AS HASH(X) MIN PARTITIONS 3 MAX PARTITIONS 3 USING com.sap.spark.engines

%vorathrift
CREATE PARTITION SCHEME DOC_STORE_PS USING DOC_STORE_PF USING com.sap.spark.engines
%vorathriftCREATE COLLECTION PRODUCT_REVIEWSPARTITION BY DOC_STORE_PS("RATINGS")USING com.sap.spark.enginesOPTIONS (files "/user/vora/reviews.json", storagebackend "hdfs")

%vorathrift
``select {"Product Id":"product_id"},{"Product Name":"product_name"},{"Customer":"customer_details.name"},{"Comment":"comment_text"},{"Stars":"rating"} from PRODUCT_REVIEWS  order by "rating"``
  USING com.sap.spark.engines

%vorathrift
``select {"Product Name":"product_name"},{"Customer":"customer_details.name"},{"Comment":"comment_text"},{"Rating":"rating"} from PRODUCT_REVIEWS where "comment_text" IS MISSING``
  USING com.sap.spark.engines

%vorathrift
SELECT SubSelect.PARTNERID ,COMPANYNAME, PHONENUMBER, EMAILADDRESS
FROM BUSINESS_PARTNER_REL
INNER JOIN ( ``SELECT ("customer_details"."id") AS PARTNERID
FROM PRODUCT_REVIEWS`` USING com.sap.spark.engines) SubSelect
ON BUSINESS_PARTNER_REL.PARTNERID = SubSelect.PARTNERID
